headline: Tyler Technologies Recognized for National Innovation, Culture, and Workplace Awards
summary: PLANO, Texas, December 18, 2025--Tyler Technologies announced today that it has been recognized with 12 industry workplace awards further recognizing Tyler's sustained leadership.
